
<!-- Header -->
<header>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="intro-text">
            <div class="intro-lead-in">Healthy Premium Japanese Rice Bowl Right Away</div>
            <div class="intro-heading">Hackmai</div>
            <button class="btn btn-xl" id="order-link">Start Ordering</button>
            <p class="large text-center intro-desc">
             Hackmai will deliver <strong>healthy authentic and original Donburi(丼, Japanese rice bowl)</strong> crafted by experienced Japanese chef <strong>within 30 minutes</strong> to your place. We will be offering weekly rotating menu of 3 donburi that only use <strong>high quality Japanese rice</strong> and ingredients. <br />Be ready to taste the extraordinary donburi in Chicago! (Beta Launch - Delivery limited to Chicago loop area)</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</header>

<!-- Order direction -->
<section id="services">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-lg-12 text-center">
                <h2 class="section-heading">How do I order?</h2>
                <h3 class="section-subheading text-muted">Order Healthy Smart Japanese Bowl in 3 easy steps!</h3>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row text-center">
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <span class="fa-stack fa-4x">
                    <i class="fa fa-circle fa-stack-2x text-primary"></i>
                    <i class="fa fa-dot-circle-o fa-stack-1x fa-inverse"></i>
                </span>
                <h4 class="service-heading">1. Choose your Bowl</h4>
                <p class="text-muted">Choose from our exclusive Japanese rice bowls selections. All of our bowls are crafted by exprience Japanese chef.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <span class="fa-stack fa-4x">
                    <i class="fa fa-circle fa-stack-2x text-primary"></i>
                    <i class="fa fa-credit-card fa-stack-1x fa-inverse"></i>
                </span>
                <h4 class="service-heading">2. Make a payment</h4>
                <p class="text-muted">After selecting your favorite bowls make a payment with your credit card.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <span class="fa-stack fa-4x">
                    <i class="fa fa-circle fa-stack-2x text-primary"></i>
                    <i class="fa fa-cutlery fa-stack-1x fa-inverse"></i>
                </span>
                <h4 class="service-heading">3. Receive a call and get ready to eat!</h4>
                <p class="text-muted">Recieve three minutes warning call and be ready to pick up your bowl. Enjoy the bowls and be productive!</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

